name: JavaSeis Examples
tagline: Examples for using JavaSeis for seismic data processing and imaging
body:
### Welcome to JavaSeis Examples
This project provides examples for using JavaSeis as a development platform for applications in seismic data processing and imaging.

See the JavaSeis wiki page for more information on setup and usage.

Chuck Mosher
